{
  "message": "build: add //go:build cgo tags to all test files and extract migrate helpers\n\nAll cmd/bd tests depend on the Dolt storage backend which requires CGO\n(for ICU). Gate tests behind cgo build tag so they cleanly skip when\nCGO is unavailable rather than failing at link time.\n\nExtract listDoltMigrations() into build-tag-conditional helpers\n(migrate_helpers_cgo.go / migrate_helpers_nocgo.go) so migrate.go\ncompiles without CGO.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
